## Body Armour, Shields ##
##########################
Show
  ItemLevel >= 84
  BaseDefencePercentile >= 90
  Rarity <= Rare
  BaseType "Full Dragonscale" "Cardinal Round Shield"
  SetFontSize 40
  SetBackgroundColor 101 8 214 255 # Bases BG Colour
  SetBorderColor 255 0 0 255
  MinimapIcon 1 Yellow Star

